# Hosting Labs
- This sequence compiles the elm app, installs the output, and then hosts the result.
``` md
``` host call
define a_host           clear    .text   empty
define b_host           process  .symbol compile_elm
define c_host           install  .symbol portal
define d_host           app_host .symbol dev_box
```

- Sets the address to host the app to `localhost:3000`
``` md
``` dev_box app_host
add address                      .text   localhost:3000
```

- Installs the "portal" app for the dev_box lab, in this case uses the optimized version.
``` md
``` portal install 
add work_dir                      .text   design/dev_box
add file_src                      .text   lib/elm/portal/elm.min.js
``` 

- This process compiles the elm app
